  "prompt": "What is the purpose of compression shorts?",
  "response": "Compression shorts serve several purposes:\n\n1. Muscle support\n- Provide support to muscles during physical activity\n- Help reduce muscle vibration and fatigue\n- Can improve muscle efficiency and performance\n\n2. Injury prevention\n- Reduce risk of muscle strain\n- Provide added stability to muscles and joints\n- Help minimize muscle movement during exercise\n\n3. Blood circulation\n- Improve blood flow to muscles\n- Help reduce muscle soreness\n- Potentially speed up recovery after exercise\n\n4. Moisture management\n- Wick away sweat from the body\n- Help keep athletes cool and dry\n- Reduce chafing and skin irritation\n\n5. Temperature regulation\n- Help keep muscles warm during exercise\n- Can provide insulation in cooler environments\n- Help prevent muscle stiffness\n\n6. Athletic performance\n- May improve athletic performance\n- Can enhance muscle power and reduce muscle oscillation\n- Often used in sports like running, cycling, and weightlifting\n\n7. Post-workout recovery\n- Aid in muscle recovery after intense exercise\n- Help reduce muscle soreness\n- Potentially decrease recovery time\n\nCompression shorts are commonly used by athletes, fitness enthusiasts, and individuals seeking muscle support during physical activities.",
